   Technology:
   NASA Hopes to Get Its Shuttles Flying Soon,
   After Grounding Fleet Due to Fuel Leaks
   ----
   By Bob Davis
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/02/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   PH ROK
</CO>
